content:
Create an opportunity history report.
On the Analytics tab, select Create | Report, or on the Reports tab, click New Report.
Select Opportunities | Opportunities with Historical Trending.
Enable Historical Trend Reporting for Opportunities in Setup.
Extend the report to all opportunities and a date range of interest.
In the report table, click the down arrow in the headers of the Amount (Historical) and the Amount columns. Click Summarize, then select Sum.
Click Run Report.
Observe the difference between the total value of the Amount (Historical) column and that of the Amount column.

You’ve created a simple historical trending report that can help you analyze your pipeline’s behavior.
title: Create Historical Trend Reports
